modName: Transmute Corundum Ingot to Dwarven Metal
summary: New spell based off the original transmute spell.
descriptionHtml:
What it says in the title.
Based off the original transmute spell but doesn\'t replace anything pre-existing.
The spell can be bought at alteration spellbook vendors as  an adept (50 alt.) spellbook.
Magicka cost, exp gain and book price is slightly more than the original transmute but still affordable.
author: Edokage
